# Telegram Jellyfin Bot

A Telegram bot to download videos to a Plex server.

## Installation

```sh
pip install telegram_jellyfin_bot
```

## Pre

The following environemnt variables are expected in-order to use this bot:

API_ID
API_HASH
TELEGRAM_API_TOKEN
MEDIA_BASE_PATH
